### PoPunkouterSoftware — API Tests
### Run these with the REST Client extension (Ctrl+Alt+R) or JetBrains HTTP Client
### Server must be running: F5 in VS Code or `dotnet run --project PoPunkouterSoftware/PoPunkouterSoftware.csproj`

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

# ─── Health ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/health — probe all external connections (Key Vault, Table Storage)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### GET /health — alias for /api/health (same handler)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── Config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/config — returns API base URL + isMockMode flag for the WASM client
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/config
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── Azure Report ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/diag/report — load latest Azure report (Table Storage then local file fallback)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/report
Accept: application/json

###

### POST /api/diag/refresh — trigger live Azure SDK background refresh (202 Accepted immediately)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### GET /api/diag/refresh-progress — poll during a running refresh
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/refresh-progress
Accept: application/json

###

### GET /api/diag/az-status — check whether a valid Azure credential exists locally
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/az-status
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── AI Fix Plans ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/diag/fix-plan/{serviceName} — AI-powered repair steps for a broken App Service
### Requires FeatureFlags:EnableAiIntegration=true + AzureOpenAI config. Cached 6h.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/fix-plan/my-app-service-name
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── GitHub Activity ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/github-activity — last commit date + 8-week sparkline for a public repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github-activity?repo=punkouter/PoPunkouterSoftware
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── Infrastructure / CI-CD Review ───────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/infra/cicd-review — scans all owned GitHub repos for CI/CD workflows & IaC definitions
### Requires GitHub:PersonalAccessToken or `gh auth login`. Cached 6h.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/infra/cicd-review
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── OpenAPI / Scalar ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /openapi/v1.json — raw OpenAPI 3.x spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Scalar interactive UI (open in browser)
# http://localhost:5000/scalar

###
